data.description: "Price Improvement" This lovely two-bedroom, two and half-bath condominium is just under 1,300 sq ft, located in the highly sought-after community “The Hammocks.” As you walk into the home, you will notice a beautiful newly installed Pergo Flooring covering the entire living/dining room. The kitchen has been updated to include a lovely backsplash, Pergo flooring, and a gorgeous LG refrigerator with a see-through glass door. The kitchen also has many counter and cabinet spaces for cooking and storage. The first level is the living/dining area, with an updated half-bathroom. Upstairs, the spacious master bedroom has a lovely bathroom with dual sinks. The second bedroom has a bathroom and a walk-in closet. The laundry room has shelving over the washer/dryer and is located on the second level near the two bedrooms. The townhouse features a clubhouse, a community fitness center, and a swimming pool. The maintenance fee covers the grounds, the exterior, and the swimming pool. All the appliances are included with the sale of the home, including a newly installed water softener. The home is close to I-75, “The Shops at Wiregrass,” and the Outlet Mall. The home is also close to many fine restaurants, hospitals (VA, Moffitt Baycare), and minutes to the airport.  Hurry, this lovely, well-taken care-of-home won’t last long.
